{"tid":891842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫光光抗爭！裸女街頭喊「習近平滾下台！」　網友同情感慨","createTime":"2018-11-06T12:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T09:26:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21b8207e69d810594063211ac05648a2ad4ddf9d","tid":891842,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lifang072/status/1059167730249752577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifang072%2Fstatus%2F1059167730249752577&d=9jSc1ZC4ThE71foaum4ATo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0622a481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifang072%2Fstatus%2F1059167730249752577&h=85fc7f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lifang072/status/1059167730249752577</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n大陸重慶街頭日前出現一名全裸女子，在人潮眾多的鬧區高喊：「打倒共產黨，還我公道，習近平滾下台」，周圍不少民眾全驚呆，紛紛好奇駐足觀看。該影片在網路發酵後，有網友感嘆女子真可憐，「要全身光溜溜，才能讓人看到妳的訴求。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/06/1627294-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F1627294-XXL.jpg&h=539dc3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子一絲不掛在鬧區高喊「打倒共產黨」、「習近平滾下台」等口號。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n4日推特上出現一則影片，一名女子全身赤裸，一絲不掛地在鬧區高喊口號：「打倒共產黨，還我公道，習近平滾下台」，有人上前幫女子披衣服，卻被她一把扔掉，隨著圍觀民眾越來越多，警方和保全也紛紛出面維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/06/1627292-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F1627292-XXL.jpg&h=bca0661d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲多名穿黑衣的警察圍上前。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n影片PO上推特後，引發網友熱烈討論，有網友好奇地問「到底發生什麼事，才會讓人民無尊嚴的去討公道」，也有人留言「真可憐，要全身光溜溜才能讓人看到妳的訴求」、「悲哀，非要用這樣來做抗爭，頂多被當做神經病」、「激烈痛苦的表達，那是沒有選擇的選擇。」（編輯：鄭餘蓉）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=452686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D452686&d=9jSc1ZC4ThE71foaum4ATo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4ffe98bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D452686&h=ea5c99a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=452686</a>"},{"pid":"7ec67e4697ce3e28c830d7f7f6ab3a66dcccf129","tid":891842,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"無格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392288db98e7f5a3ce570c4f5ea51057f831f72b","tid":891842,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"RIP 來生不做蚛蟈人"},{"pid":"98f2d0805a071b8870d3a79a5a15cf1ccdbedac1","tid":891842,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}